    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive mechanical vetting, including a full valvetrain adjustment and documented subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing linear power delivery and exceptional tactile feedback. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or paint failure, while the interior remains in a preserved state with supple Nappa leather. Every bushing, gasket, and fluid has been maintained to concourse standards, resulting in a vehicle that performs exactly as it did when it left Regensburg.",
